  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT28">
<l>teṉṉilaṅkai yaraṇcitaṟi yavuṇaṉ māḷac</l>
<l>ceṉṟulaka mūṉṟiṉaiyun tirintōr tērāl</l>
<l>maṉṉilaṅku pāratattai māḷa vūrnta</l>
<l>varaiyuruviṉ mākaḷiṟṟait tōḻī yeṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉilaṅku mulaikkuvaṭṭil pūṭṭik koṇṭu</l>
<l>pōkāmai vallēṉāyp pulavi yeyti</l>
<l>eṉṉilaṅka mellāmvan tiṉpa meyta</l>
<l>veppoḻutum niṉainturuki yiruppaṉ nāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[That] massive mountain-shaped bull elephant who drove a chariot</l>
<l rend="indent">to end the great, renowned Bhārata [War],</l>
<l>Wandering the three worlds, arriving so that the demon died,</l>
<l rend="indent">scattering the defenses of southern Lanka,</l>
<l>Friend, as one who is without strength [to keep him] from going,</l>
<l rend="indent">[by] clasping [him] to the mounds of my breasts of pallid glow,</l>
<l>Reaching a pique, [but] thinking of [him] always so that delight reaches [me]</l>
<l rend="indent">arriving [in] every limb on me, I am tender[-hearted].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
